title: Manton, New South Wales
text: Manton is a locality in the <a href="Yass%20Valley%20Council">Yass Valley Council</a>, <a href="New%20South%20Wales">New South Wales</a>, Australia. It lies on both sides of both the <a href="Hume%20Highway">Hume Highway</a> and the <a href="Barton%20Highway">Barton Highway</a> to the east of their intersection about 10 km to the east of <a href="Yass%2C%20New%20South%20Wales">Yass</a>. At the , it had a population of 294.
